title: Orgasmic
typeOfFood: Lacto, Mediterranean, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Greek, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small kiosk style restaurant situated in an alley way next to other veg-friendly restaurants. Busy during weekends and evenings. Offers a Middle Eastern menu. Falafel is vegan, and platters are available in vegan when requests. Has salads, tabouli, hummus, and sides like pita, olives, pickles, sauerkraut, salsa, and cabbage.
